</sense> <sense n="2" xml:id="D2"> <lbl expand="concretus, e (opp.&#xA;                            abstracto)">concr.</lbl>, <gramGrp> <gen value="femininus">fem.</gen> </gramGrp> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ረድእት፡</foreign> (<ref cRef="Act." loc="9,36">Act. 9,36</ref> Platt; F.N. 22; <ref cRef="Sx. Genb." loc="20 ">Sx. Genb. 20 </ref>Enc.), <lbl expand="pluralis">Pl.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርዳእ፡</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርድእት፡</foreign>, adjutor i.e. <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> famulus </quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> minister </quote></cit> <ref cRef="Matth." loc="13,27">Matth. 13,27</ref>; F.N. 8,3 ubi <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንፍቀ፡ ዲያቆን፡</foreign> exponitur <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርድእት፡</foreign>; et plerumque <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> discipulus </quote></cit> (<foreign xml:lang="grc">μαθητής</foreign>) magistri, ut: prophetae <ref cRef="Jsp." loc="301,">Jsp. p. 301,</ref> monachi <ref cRef="Phlx." loc="85,">Phlx. 85,</ref> Joannis baptistae <ref cRef="Matth." loc="14,12">Matth. 14,12</ref>; <ref cRef="Marc." loc="6,29">Marc. 6,29</ref>; <ref cRef="Mosis Joh." loc="9,28">Mosis Joh. 9,28</ref>; <ref cRef="Pharisaeorum Matth." loc="22,16">Pharisaeorum Matth. 22,16</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ረድኦሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Haim. Ab. " loc="2">Haim. Ab.  2</ref>-5; in specie Christi: <ref cRef="Joh." loc="9,27">Joh. 9,27</ref>; <ref cRef="Joh." loc="19,38">Joh. 19,38</ref>; <ref cRef="Luc." loc="14,26">Luc. 14,26</ref>; <ref cRef="Act." loc="6,1">Act. 6,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Act." loc="9,25">Act. 9,25</ref>; <ref cRef="Act. " loc="21,16">Act.  21,16</ref>; <ref cRef="Did." loc="10">Did. 10</ref>; duodecim <ref cRef="Matth." loc="10,1">Matth. 10,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Matth." loc="11,1">Matth. 11,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Matth." loc="12,1">Matth. 12,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Luc." loc="17,1">Luc. 17,1</ref> al.; Asc. <ref cRef="Jes." loc="3,13">Jes. 3,13</ref>; <ref cRef="Asc. Jes." loc="3,17">Asc. Jes. 3,17</ref>; <ref cRef="Asc. Jes." loc="11,22">Asc. Jes. 11,22</ref>. Deinde in libris Aethiopum creberrime memorantur septuaginta duo vel septuaginta discipuli Christi secundum <ref cRef="Luc." loc="10,1">Luc. 10,1</ref>; <ref cRef="Luc." loc="10,17">Luc. 10,17</ref>, ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">፸ወ፪አርድእት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Lit." loc="164,2">Lit. 164,2</ref>; <ref cRef="Sx. Teq." loc="14">Sx. Teq. 14</ref>; <ref cRef="Sx. Teq." loc="26">Sx. Teq. 26</ref>; <ref cRef="Genz." loc="151">Genz. f. 151</ref>; Haim. Ab.; <foreign xml:lang="gez">፸፡</foreign> Deg.; Sx. <ref cRef="Teq." loc="26 ">Teq. 26 </ref>Enc. 
</sense> </sense>
               
